title: Penguins
description: Blippi wonders can penguins fly?

title: Pajama Pajimjams
description: Oscar pretends to be a talking pair of pajamas named "Jimjams" to make his friend Pajamas happy.

title: The Trouble with Truth
description: The JLA find themselves in danger of losing Wonder Woman when the goddess Athena comes to Earth with an offer Diana can't refuse, filling the position of the Goddess of Truth on Mt. Olympus.

title: Huevos de bote
description: Tratando de evitar ser asustados durante la Pascua, los Titanes eliminan al Conejo de Pascua y se encargan ellos mismos de la festividad.

title: Flush Hour
description: The babies learn the purpose of toilets.

title: Up in the Air
description: After he causes the Batwing to crash, Bam becomes obsessed with making it up to her during a high-stakes aerial mission against Penguin and his giant ducky blimp.

title: A Patch of Perturbed Petunias
description: Share fears she's losing her ability as a problem-solver and peacemaker when she can't calm a squabble between a group of Whiffles and a flower bed of Perturbed Petunias. Cheer discovers it's not Share's fault; the Petunias are being secretly manipulated by Bluster's rumor-mongering.

title: Ant We All Just Get Along
description: Owen and Beth try to save an ant hill that Courtney and Leshawna want to destroy.

title: Final Battle! Dan vs. Ajit/Secrets Exposed
description: Final Battle! Dan vs. Ajit: It's time for the event everyone in Los Volmos has been waiting for, The Bakugan Battle League finals! It's the Awesome Brawler's Dan Kouzo vs. the golden Bakugan brawler Ajit, these two face-off in a final brawl for it all./Secrets Exposed: The Bakugan Battle League has ended, and the winner has been determined, but the celebration is cut short when Phantom Thief Storm crashes the party by stealing everyone's Bakugan! It's up to Dan and Ajit to stop Storm and return all the stolen Bakugan.

title: Haunted Campfire
description: The campers must battle ghosts of their own creation after their scary stories mysteriously come true.

title: Double Cross
description: Batman has Plastic Man disguise himself as Two-Face in order to set a trap for Deadshot. Unfortunately things get complicated when the real Two-Face escapes custody.

title: La Formula de Manzana
description: Manzana necesita encontrar una fórmula divertida que le permita conseguir un papel cómico en una película.

title: TV Knight 8
description: Teen Titans Go takes a comedic look at the superheroes' lives. Viewers finally get the opportunity to watch what life is like for the super teens when their capes are left at home. The teens will deal with everyday issues of adolescence including laundry contests and quests to construct the perfect sandwich.

title: Triple T Tigers
description: The Bears meet three cool tiger brothers. Grizz wants to be just like the oldest Tiger, TK, but he may not be the best role model.

title: The Library
description: The campers spend a rainy day at the library.

title: That Ol' Time Rock Rolls!/Make Like a Banana and Split
description: When Big Old Boulder rolls down the hill towards the museum, Berta needs the Mechas help to keep it stable./It's Food Day in Pretty Big City, but the Mechas need to help when the banana atop the banana split statue is not split!

title: Moon Problems
description: The Moon gets sad when Oscar loses his friendship bracelet.

title: Would You Like to Enter Prime Empire?
description: While investigating a heist, the ninja discover Prime Empire, a legendary unreleased arcade game that suddenly takes control of all other games in Ninjago.

title: The Curse of Elmore
description: When Gumball's schoolfriend Leslie finds an old video tape, the creepy mystery of Elmore's ghostly past unfolds. Featuring spooky and hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Booty Eggs
description: Not wanting to be creeped out on Easter the Titans dispatch the Easter Bunny and take matters into their own hands.

title: Cellie
description: Fed up with sharing, Panda forbids his brothers from using his cellphone any longer. But when the brothers get their own super advanced smartphones, Panda starts to succumb to crippling jealousy.

title: Puff Paint
description: Oscar's painting is unpopular so he goes on a journey of self-discovery.

title: Pajamas Party
description: When Pajamas starts to panic that Oscar will outgrow her, Oscar tries to help but things go awry.

title: Director's Cut
description: Oscar receives a camcorder from his parents and sets out to prove to them the magic on the island is real.

title: Together Alone
description: Steven throws a party to bring his family together.

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: Time Traveling Quick Pants
description: Oscar and Hedgehog learn about a quicksand that lets them go back in time.

title: Cosmic Bupkiss
description: A storm blocks Oscar and Hedgehog's one chance to see a comet.

title: Unica
description: The Bears join forces with Unica, the ultimate forest protector.

title: Karate Mom
description: After surprising Clarence with Martial Arts classes at the "Aberdojo," Mary gets talked into joining the class herself. She loves the slow-paced lessons in discipline and control, but Clarence just wants to have fun and kick butt! Can Mary convince Clarence to stick with the class, earn his belt and have some fun with her?

title: Porque tan triste?
description: Steven ha escuchado rumores de un par de Gemas que todavía están destruyendo mundos. Si él no puede detenerlas, tal vez Lapis sí.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: The Big Game
description: Chad takes Clarence to his first big game! Clarence takes it all in - the crack of the bat, the touchdown dances, the slam-dunks and of course, hotdogs and popcorn! But will Clarence get to fulfill his dream of meeting Aberdale's beloved mascot?

title: Counting Cows
description: When Thomas and Percy volunteer to deliver a herd of cows, they realize that the cows keep wandering off on their own adventures unless the two friends can both pay better attention.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Mr. Gus Moves Out
description: When a fed-up Mr. Gus moves out of the RV, Uncle Grandpa and Pizza Steve work together to get him back.

title: Beyond the Rapids
description: Resident creek scientist Wren enlists Craig to voyage through dangerous waters in search of a path to the Ocean.

title: Elmore's Most Wanted
description: Gumball's dad has been revealed as "Elmore's Most Wanted" - but when the Chief of Police tries to investigate, things do not go according to plan. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Cambia de Parecer
description: Steven se enfrenta al mayor desafío de su vida.

title: Un Episodio Muy Especial
description: Cuarzo Arcoíris 2.0 prometió cuidar de Cebolla el mismo día que Heliolita programó una charla sobre la seguridad del hogar. ¿Es posible para Steven estar en dos lugares a la vez y ser dos fusiones al mismo tiempo?

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Cual Reloj?
description: Cuando una batalla con Kevin queda interrumpida, Ben se concentra en ser mejor que Gwen en el Campamento Espacial. Pero cuando Kevin regresa con la mirada extrañamente puesta en su prima, nuestro héroe debe descubrir quién está realmente detrás de todo esto: iCharmcaster!

title: La Conciencia
description: Gumball y Darwin intentan ser más ecológicos y, como consecuencia, la escuela termina infestada de enredaderas.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Battle for the Bottled City
description: Atom shrinks Superman so he can visit his fellow Kryptonians in the bottled city of Kandor. Soon after, Brainiac attacks and takes off with the bottle. Atom is forced to take control of one of Superman's damaged robots in order to follow after Brainiac and retrieve the city.

title: Monster Visit
description: The monsters get nervous when their Godmonster comes for a visit.

title: A Fistful of Brains
description: Grandpa Max and Rook are looking all over the galaxy for Ben, who is trapped on Khyber's hidden personal hunting preserve.

title: Twelve Angry Hedgehogs
description: Hedgehog wants to win the Golden Science Badge but runs into some unexpected competition.

title: Rock Show
description: Chad's band Dogmon, plays a show for the first time in years, giving Clarence and Mary a chance to really rock out.

title: Jessica the Intern
description: Entranced with the Trading Tree and Kit's business acumen, Jessica joins Kit as her intern!

title: Mutiny for the Bounty
description: While Phil and Grandpa Max tune-up the Omni-Copter, a restless Ben takes the Rustbuggy off road, but when he is suddenly captured by Textrax and the hunter takes the bounty for himself, our hero must not only escape but avoid the wrath of the double-crossed Kraab and Sixsix!

title: The Best Friend/Thief and Brawler
description: The Best Friend: The top four brawlers in the Bakugan Battle League have been decided. For this round of the semi-finals it's a battle of best friends: Wynton vs. Dan. The winner of this battle between best buddies will move on to the championship round./Thief and Brawler: In the final battle of the Bakugan Battle league semi-finals it's Shun vs. Ajit. It's a grueling battle of focus, will, and strength, only a true brawler to emerge victorious.

title: The Last Laserdisc Player
description: Mordecai, Rigby, Muscle Man and HFG want to get a laserdisc player so they can watch the director's cut of a cult classic.

title: I Strain
description: Petunia gets hooked on watching television and stops playing with her friends.

title: La Super Increible Aventura en Balsa
description: Unikitty y Hawkodile están "perdidos en el mar," varados en una balsa juntos. Hawkodile ve esto como una oportunidad para mostrarle a Unikitty que está preparado para cualquier cosa con sus habilidades de experto en supervivencia, pero para su sorpresa, todos sus planes fracasan, mientras que la tonta postura de Unikitty de "todo saldrá bien, vamos a divertirnos" está funcionando de una manera genial. ¿Será Hawkodile capaz de soltar su exceso de preparación para salvarlos a ambos, o acaso la diversión caprichosa de Unikitty será su perdición?

title: Panda's Family
description: While exploring a lantern festival, the Bears encounter Panda's long-lost family.

title: Chill Out
description: Uncle Grandpa takes a kid to the North Pole for an epic snowball battle.

title: Hustlecup
description: When Buttercup loses the Professor's latest invention, she'll have to beat The Gangreen Gang at their own game to get it back.

title: Flower Power
description: The babies all want to pick the best flowers for Granny but they end up destroying her garden.

title: Isla Dyer
description: Cuando los ninjas relacionan la desaparición de Jay con Primer Imperio, van a la Isla Dyer para buscar respuestas del diseñador del juego, Milton Dyer.

title: Follow Your Dreams
description: Apple and Onion need to find a dream to follow, so that their lives don't head nowhere.

title: Duo Espinoso
description: Después de dejar Pequeña Escuela Madre, Steven ha encontrado un nuevo pasatiempo: las plantas.

title: Space Invasion
description: A visit from Puddle the alien tests the limit of Oscar's hosting skills.

title: Bebe Baktu
description: Cuando es atacado en la jungla, el equipo Tennyson es salvado por un niño que se parece inquietantemente a Tim Buktu, pero cuando descubren que realmente es una versión en miniatura del infame trotamundos, Ben sabe que se avecina otra amenaza, Nanny Nightmare!

title: Monkey See, Doggie Do/Mommy Fearest
description: Monkey See, Doggie Do: Mojo unleashes a curse on Townsville that turns everyone into dogs, including the Powerpuff Girls! Luckily, they manage to sniff out a solution and show Mojo that their bite is worse than his bark./Mommy Fearest: When Professor Utonium falls for the lovely Ima Goodlady, the girls quickly discover that Ima's not such a good lady after all. She's really the sinister Sedusa!

title: Dyer Island
description: When the ninja connect Jay's disappearance to Prime Empire, they set out to Dyer Island to seek answers from the game's designer, the elusive Milton Dyer.

title: Pepper's Blanket Is Missing
description: Pepper's blanket goes missing at a cabin sleepover.

title: Happy Place
description: Time to share some of the honey made at Lellobee City Farm with everyone that visits the farm

title: The Director/Queen Ebony
description: The Director: Everett Ray reaches out to Lia with an opportunity that seems too good to be true. Everett is now working in show business and proposes to make Lia's dream of becoming a film director come true. He's taken care of all the arrangements; all Lia has to do is provide the directorial vision./Queen Ebony: On his daily jaunt, Lightning learns of a street cat named Ebony, who's been treating dogs like servants, threatening them to do her bidding or face the wrath of her Bakugan! Lightning tries to reason with Ebony but when that doesn't work, it turns into a cat vs. dog Bakugan brawl!

title: OTTO Motive
description: Kevin and Rook run into an old enemy from the Null Void while attending an intergalactic auto show. (Re-introducing classic Ben alien, Upgrade.)

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Fuzzy Pink Time Babies
description: Oscar and Hedgehog learn how to stop time.

title: Escapism
description: Steven uses his psychic powers to find help.

title: El Hechizo
description: Craig, Kelsey y JP ayudan a un niño al que le lanzaron una maldición que le impide hablar, aunque pronto se arrepienten de haberlo hecho.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Baby Buktu
description: When attacked in the jungle, Team Tennyson is saved by a toddler who looks eerily similar to Tim Buktu, but when they discover it really is a pint sized version of the nefarious globetrotter, Ben knows there's another threat looming, Nanny Nightmare!

title: TV Knight 4
description: Batman and Commissioner Gordon go camping but instead of fun outdoor activities they'd rather watch TV.

title: Magnet Mayhem/Stop That Train
description: The magnet crane at the construction site accidentally turns on, sucking up all the metal, including the Mecha Builders!/Roof is delivering eggs to Marwyn at the Train Station, that is, until the train pulls into the station and can't stop!

title: A Very Percy Valentine's Day
description: It's Valentine's Day and no one on Sodor is happier than Percy -- he gets to deliver everyone's gifts to their friends throughout the island! Unfortunately, his energetic eagerness turns to panic when an accident on the rails causes everyone's presents to fall in the mud! With Thomas' help, Percy discovers a way to still deliver the feelings behind everyone's presents -- by using the gift of song!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: Compartir es querer
description: Courtney se niega a compartir su valioso juguete de coleccionista con sus amigos.

title: Mop Forever
description: At Alice's dress-up party the campers are magically turned into their costumes.

title: Them's Fightin' Words!
description: After enjoying some local corn, Team Tennyson discovers a Hartfield-McJoy reenactment in the cornfield next door, but when Hex resurrects the ghosts of the real feuding families, Ben must find a way to bring them together if he is to save the day!

title: Te Gustaria Entrar a Primer Imperio?
description: Mientras investigan un robo, los ninjas descubren Primer Imperio, un videojuego que  toma el control de todos los demás videojuegos de Ninjago.

title: Brother Builder
description: As Craig races against time to build a super important invention, we learn how Craig became such a clever inventor!

title: Computer Vampire
description: Oscar finds a mysterious old video game in the library.

title: Feeling Spacey
description: Oscar and Hedgehog arrive on a planet that has no emotions.

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: Little Graduation
description: Steven and the Gems celebrate Little Homeschool's first graduating class.

title: Rain, Rain Go Away
description: After Grumpy's anger sends his belly badge out of control with a thunderstorm that floods a newly-planted Whiffle meadow, he vows to never be grumpy again. Renaming himself "Mr. Happy," he drives everyone crazy with niceness. When the Whiffles desperately need his clouds to make rain and Mr. Happy can't deliver, Cheer and the team must get him back in touch with his inner grump.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Level Thirteen
description: Cyrus Borg discovers a shocking secret about Prime Empire, while the ninja battle an escaped Mechanic in their attempt to reach Level Thirteen and enter the game themselves.

title: Y todos nos llevamos bien
description: Owen y Beth tratan de salvar un hormiguero que Courtney y Leshawna quieren destruir.

title: Nom Nom's Entourage
description: Nom Nom recruits the Bears to act as his entourage of friends. But when the Bears realize Nom Nom doesn't understand friendship, they decide to kick their day of bonding into high gear.

title: Cone in 60 Seconds
description: After Owen gets ripped off at the ice cream truck, the kids unite to right that wrong.

title: The First Day
description: Best friends Oscar and Hedgehog get dropped off at their first day at summer camp.

title: Why So Blue?
description: Steven has heard rumors of a pair of Gems that are still destroying worlds. If he can't stop them, maybe Lapis can.

title: El Hedor
description: El Sr. Small se vuelve salvaje cuando Gumball y Darwin exponen su hipocresía.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Dino Fright
description: George P. Mandrake hires The Looney Builders to build a T. Rex fossil. It's Tweety's job to place the bones with his crane, but his fear of the big dino affects his ability to get the job done.

title: Nivel Trece
description: Cyrus Borg descubre un secreto sobre Primer Imperio y  los ninjas enfrentan al Mecánico que escapó e intenta alcanzar el Nivel 13 para entrar al juego.

title: Chair
description: Unikitty finds an old, beatup recliner on the curb, but sees its inner beauty and brings it home to introduce to the gang! In a series of absurd and fun vignettes, we discover how a dirty, inanimate chair comes into each of their lives and changes them for the better. We soon learn that dear, sweet Chair was too good for this world.

title: The Bike Ride
description: Pizza Steve desperately tries to prevent the gang from finding out his shameful secret.

title: Perricornio Patinador
description: Puppycorn quiere impresionar a sus amigos patinadores con sus habilidades fantásticas, el problema es que no tiene ninguna. Con la esperanza de aumentar su confianza, Unikitty y la pandilla se ponen los trajes invisibles de la Dra. Fox para ayudarlo secretamente a realizar movimientos imposibles. Pero hacen su trabajo demasiado bien y el "patinador profesional" Puppycorn está invitado a mostrar sus habilidades en una peligrosa competencia de escenas de riesgo. ¿Hasta dónde llegará la pandilla para ayudar al cachorro a realizar sus sueños inalcanzables e increíbles?

title: For a Few Brains More
description: Ben, Rook and Max must stop Ultimate Albedo from absorbing Azmuth's intelligence and taking over the galaxy.

title: River of Gold
description: Apple and Onion find a mysterious book but they better read it fast before it disappears forever.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: Popular Banana Split
description: Hedgehog and Max discover a tiny high school when they are accidentally shrunk by a science experiment.

title: Lightning Bugs Sylvester
description: Sylvester learns to overcome his fear of lightning.

title: The Buddy
description: Anais and school psycho Jamie are accused of the same techno-crime. They are forced to team up to discover the real culprit in order to prove their innocence. After solving the case, they realize that they have more in common than they thought...

title: Garden of Evil
description: Poison Ivy takes control of Swamp Thing using his vegetative powers to overwhelm Gotham with dangerous plants.

title: Copycat Carter
description: Craig and his friends stumble upon Carter, the cardboard genius turned cyborg, and Craig decides to help Carter become a kid again, just like him!

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

title: Blippi Learns Rainbow Colors
description: Have you ever wondered how a rainbow gets its colors? Join Blippi and his sidekick TABBS on their first adventure as they discover the science behind rainbows!

title: Chicken and Waffles
description: Panda needs to meet his brothers at the most exclusive restaurant in town. But when he loses his contacts lenses and can't see, Panda needs Charlie's help to get him into the city.

title: Chocolate Money Badgers
description: Oscar learns that he can earn merit badges that unlock prizes.

title: The Boxcurse Children
description: Clarence, Jeff, and Sumo stumble upon a mysterious box. After they open it, some strange things begin to happen. Convinced they've unlocked a curse, they become determined to reverse it!

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Slip
description: Richard doesn't answer the door in time and the jobsworth delivery guy will not let him have his package. His options are to pick his package up at the depot or pay for a redelivery. Richard doesn't like the sound of either option, so a battle of wills begins that can only end in the destruction of one or both of them.

title: Conquistando torres
description: Duncan, Leshawna y Jude quieren una pieza de esquina del pastel de cumpleaños de Izzy, pero, ¿están preparados para hacer cualquier cosa por conseguir uno?

title: Superstar Rockin' Jay
description: Now inside the Prime Empire game, the ninja find themselves in unfamiliar territory, ignorant of the rules of this world, as they try to find Zane and escape Unagami's army of Red Visors.

title: I See a Funny Cartoon in Your Future/Octi-Gone
description: I See a Funny Cartoon In Your Future: The girls have the rare task of fighting a medium who is committing petty thefts./Octi-gone: When Bubbles finds a single leg of Octi's, she sets out to find out who took her toy and what they want from her.

title: Brawl Bot
description: Dr. Fox is proud to unveil her new ultimate combat machine and take it into an underground scientist fighting ring. But Hawkodile's jealous of Dr. Fox's fighting bot that's supposedly a better puncher than him and declares he can beat anything it can. To prove his point, he dresses up in spare robot parts and enters himself secretly in the bot battle. With Unikitty as his fighting coach, can Hawkodile survive the tourney, prove he's tougher than a machine, and avoid the scrap yard?

title: Vote Gumball…and Penny?
description: Gumball is running for School President and is looking for a worthy running mate. When he asks his girlfriend Penny, he does not get the answer he expects. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Mother's Day
description: Gumball, Darwin and Anais need to find the perfect Mother's Day gift. Will it be a cute card, a thoughtful painting or something entirely different? Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Soundhouse
description: Oscar and Hedgehog discover a new structure on the island and become friends with its caretaker.

title: Perfect Day
description: Ben thinks he's having 'the perfect day' only to realize he's been put in a dream world by Enoch and the Forever Knights who are after the Omnitrix. Ben's "dream world" soon becomes a nightmare world, with Ben forced to live out his ultimate terror...being stuck at school! But with Max and Gwen's help, he's able to vanquish his nightmare foes and re-enter the real world where he takes down  Enoch...only to reveal an even more powerful knight...The Forever King.

title: Web Weirdos
description: When Finn gets trapped in a giant spider web, he ends up playing marriage counselor to a couple of grumpy arachnids.

title: Valentine's Hearts
description: As the other engines prepare for a Valentine's Day party, Kana is worried: she doesn't know what to bring! Inspired by Sandy's giant metal heart surprise, Kana decides that she is going to create a sparkly big heart using her electricity! Through a series of accidents, Kana realizes that the best surprise she could bring to the party is herself!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Rio de Oro
description: Manzana y Cebolla intentan terminar un cuento antes de que el libro desaparezca para siempre.

title: I Heart Heartforde
description: Oscar, hedgehog and the other campers are excited to take a trip to the non-magical town of Heartforde.

title: Campers Above the Bed
description: Hedgehog finds a city underneath her bed as she looks for her missing diary.

title: Roughing It Up/What's the Big Idea?
description: Roughing It Up: The girls and the Professor set out on an old-fashioned vacation to the Townsville Swamp. Trouble is, Fuzzy and his nephews are there, too./What's the Big Idea?: 20 story high Powerpuff Girls spell disaster for Townsville when they delicately try to stop Mojo from taking over.

title: Leader of the Pack
description: Daffy starts a secret password club for everyone except Bugs.

title: Sigue Tus Suenos
description: Manzana y Cebollín necesitan encontrar un sueño que perseguir para que sus vidas tengan un rumbo.

title: Return to Forever
description: The Forever Knights threaten to use a sinister weapon to erase all alien DNA on Earth unless Ben and Rook can stop them.

title: Subway
description: The Bears are stranded on a subway platform after missing their train. But while waiting, the Bears are challenged with recovering some lost items.

title: Escapismo
description: Steven usa sus poderes psíquicos para conseguir ayuda.

title: Brainlord
description: A new superhero arrives in Townsville with a dark secret.

title: The Ultimate Heist
description: Albedo seeks a device that will finally change him back into his Galvan form; meanwhile, Ben is locked in Plumber HQ prison.

title: Big Trouble Little Babies
description: When they realize they're too small for the rides at an amusement park, the Bears use a magic potion to get bigger.

title: A Yoorg Awakening
description: Funshine's jokes unwittingly hurt the feelings of a strange Rock Giant. Disturbed from its slumber, the usually benign creature inadvertently creates havoc for the Whiffles until Funshine calms it by apologizing.

title: A Wide Delivery
description: When the trains must deliver in pairs, Thomas is disappointed to be paired with Diesel instead of his BFF Percy.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Ice Cream Headache
description: The campers get magical powers from the witches supply of magic ice cream.

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: Pool's Out for Summer
description: The boys go to the Aberdale Community Pool for a day of wet fun! While Jeff slowly wades in the shallow end, getting used to the water, Sumo tries to conquer the diving board, redeeming himself from last summer's bellyflop, and Clarence sneaks past the lifeguards into the hot tub for a boiling surprise.

title: Tasty Heist
description: Richard's prepared one of the tastiest desserts ever, but he's locked it up tight until the friends have their boring dinner. This will not stand. Unikitty organizes a heist, assembling the friends as a crack team to get in, get out, and eat that tasty snack without Richard knowing. But this heist has hiccups. Can the friends take the cake?

title: Rebel Rebel
description: The Professor makes new friends, but they may be the wrong crowd.

title: Sandy's Sandy Shipment
description: When Sandy learns about a massive shipment of sand that needs to be delivered, she is determined to help despite her size.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: Here Comes Haavik/The Fusion Bakugan Arrive
description: Here Comes Haavik: An evil shapeshifting alien has landed in Los Volmos! If that wasn't bad enough, he has a group of robot mechanoids on his trail trying to bring him justice. Meanwhile, Dan has accepted a battle challenge from a pair of brawlers, Chad and Trey./The Fusion Bakugan Arrive: Still humiliated by their defeat, Chad and Trey challenge Dan to rematch but this time they have a few tricks up their sleeve, and a little help on their side.

title: CN Special: NBA All-Star Slam Dunk Contest
description: Cartoon Network's version of the NBA Slam Dunk Contest, highlighting the best slam dunks, hosted by the Teen Titans.

title: Pollo y Waffles
description: Panda debe encontrarse con sus hermanos en el restaurant más exclusivo de la ciudad. Pero cuando pierde sus lentes de contacto y no ve nada, Panda necesita la ayuda de Charlie para llegar a la ciudad.

title: O'Little Tree
description: Mei shows Ella and Rishi the magic of Christmas - by growing an adorable Christmas tree in the middle of the farm.

title: Caballero televisivo 4
description: Batman y el comisionado Gordon van de campamento, pero en lugar de hacer actividades divertidas al aire libre, prefieren ver televisión.

title: The Awareness
description: Gumball tries to convince Leslie he's an expert on all things plant-related. However, when Leslie realizes Gumball hasn't got a clue what he's talking about, he decides to call his bluff. An escalation of dangerous dares and stunts ensue as they try to out-plant each other.

title: The Son of Lilly
description: The battle for the fate of Shintaro Mountain concludes!

title: Germ Factory
description: After seeing Leshawna enjoying a sick day at home with ice cream and TV, Duncan convinces the other kids try to get sick too.

title: El Recibo
description: Papá pierde un paquete y se ve envuelto en una pelea cada vez mayor con el repartidor.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Hug Wolf
description: After an encounter with a Hug Wolf, Finn goes through a Jekyll and Hyde-like transformation becoming a hug-wolf himself!

title: Insect Inside/Powerpuff Bluff
description: Insect Inside: Vile villain Roach Coach has a plan to infest Townsville with an army of cockroaches! The girls overcome their squirms to squash Roach Coach's scheme and force him to bug off./Powerpuff Bluff: Three local hoods get new identities when they find grown-up-sized Powerpuff costumes inside Townsville Jail. They terrorize Townsville while the Mayor mistakenly sends the real girls to the slammer.

title: The Stink
description: Gumball decides to put Mr. Small's eco-friendly principles to the test but it doesn't quite go as planned. Mr. Small disappears after deciding to leave the modern world behind. But on the plus side they discover that the Great Stink-Ape of Elmore Woods is definitely not extinct.

title: Susie's Fantastical Scavenger Hunt
description: Oscar and Hedgehog must learn to exist without each other when they are put on different teams during a scavenger hunt.

title: In Your Footsteps
description: A bear befriends Finn and Jake, but what are his true intentions?

title: Saxophone Come Home
description: Oscar befriends a teenage Yeti.

title: Pelea Bot
description: La Dra. Fox se enorgullece de presentar su nueva máquina de combate definitiva y llevarla a un ring de combate científico subterráneo. Pero Hawkodile está celoso del bot de combate de la Dra. Fox, que supuestamente da mejores golpes que él, y declara que puede vencer a cualquier cosa que el bot pueda. Para demostrar su afirmación, se viste con piezas de robot de repuesto y entra en secreto en la batalla de robots. Con Unikitty como su entrenadora de lucha, ¿podrá Hawkodile sobrevivir al torneo, demostrar que es más fuerte que una máquina y salvarse del depósito de chatarra?

title: Hermano Constructor
description: Craig juega una carrera contra el tiempo para construir un invento superimportante. Mientras tanto, nos enteramos de cómo fue que Craig se volvió un inventor tan ingenioso.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Jay Estrella del Rock
description: Dentro de Primer Imperio, los ninjas se encuentran en un territorio desconocido e intentan encontrar a Jay y escapar de los Visores Rojos de Unagami.

title: Salchichas y Dulce Golpe
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben superar sus obsesiones por las salchichas y los videojuegos.

title: Anger Management
description: In order to appear on a successful kids show, Nom Nom must successfully complete anger management, with Grizz as his partner.

title: Super Amazing Raft Adventure
description: Unikitty and Hawkodile are "lost at sea", stranded on a raft together. Hawkodile sees this as an opportunity to show Unikitty that he's prepared for anything with his expertly-honed survival skills, but to his shock, all of his plans keep falling apart, while Unikitty's silly "it'll all work out, let's have fun" approach is somehow working great! Will Hawkodile manage to let go of his overpreparedness to save them both, or will Unikitty whimsical fun be their doom?

title: Trailer Trashed
description: Muscle Man's trailer fails a health inspection and he wants to keep it at all costs.

title: Sharing Is Caring
description: Courtney refuses to share her valuable collectors item toy with her classmates.

title: Huelga por el Botin
description: Mientras Phil y el abuelo Max afinan el Omni-Copter, Ben, inquieto, saca el Rustbuggy de la carretera. Pero cuando de repente es capturado por Tetrax, nuestro héroe no solo debe escapar, sino también evitar la ira de los traicioneros Kraab y SeiSeis.

title: Hiccup Havok
description: Uncle Grandpa helps a kid who can't get rid of the hiccups.

title: Sophie, the Bakuganist/Midnight Train Battle!
description: Sophie, the Bakuganist: Magnus is on the trail of the illegal Baku-brawling devices and, is looking to cut off the supply at its source. When he witnesses an illegal deal going down, he knows it's up to him to go after the shipment to keep the illegal devices off the street./Midnight Train Battle!: Sophie Judson Warfield, a wealthy activist with the Citizens to Save Bakugan Society, is working to put an end to all Bakugan brawling. Her latest target is the Awesome Brawlers themselves. When Wynton doesn't take Sophie seriously, the encounter quickly turns into an all-out Bakugan brawl.

title: Fabrica de germenes
description: Después de ver a Leshawna disfrutar de un día enferma en casa con helado y TV, Duncan convence a los otros chicos de que traten de enfermarse.

title: El Drama
description: Gumball intenta proteger a Darwin de Carrie, su inapropiada novia fantasma.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: El metro
description: Luego de perder el tren, los Osos quedan varados en una plataforma del subterráneo. Pero mientras esperan, se desafían a recuperar algunos objetos perdidos.

title: Blippi Saves Christmas
description: Blippi wonders how does Santa know where we live?

title: Lil' Dimples
description: Thinking it's a way to reconnect with her father, Raven enters a beauty pageant.

title: Cuttin' Corners
description: Duncan, Leshawna and Jude all want corner pieces of Izzy's Birthday Cake… But are they prepared to go to any length to get one?

title: La Moneda De La Suerte
description: Craig y sus amigos se encuentran con Carter, el genio de cartón convertido en androide, y Craig decide ayudar a Carter a volver a ser niño igual que él.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Dia de Nevada
description: Steven y las Gemas de Cristal tienen la oportunidad de ponerse al día en un día nevado.

title: Sausage and Sweetie Smash
description: Onion must stop Apple from falling prey to his obsession, but a certain phone game is proving to be quite an obstacle.

title: Return to the Nightosphere
description: Marceline's dad banishes Finn and Jake to the Nightosphere, and it stinks. Literally.

title: Race Track Race
description: The Looney Builders race against the clock to build Cecil Turtle a new racetrack. Daffy gets caught up in his own desire to race and changes part of the build.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Inside Job
description: In a "Fantastic Voyage" like adventure, Atom shrinks Batman and Wonder Woman so they can enter Superman's bloodstream and destroy a lethal nanite virus.

title: Maiz Peleas
description: El equipo Tennyson descubre una reconstrucción del conflicto familiar Hartfield-McJoy en el maizal de al lado, pero cuando Hex resucita a los fantasmas de las verdaderas familias enemistadas, Ben debe encontrar la manera de reunirlos si quiere salvar a todos.

title: Pequena graduacion
description: Steven y las Gemas celebran la primera clase de graduados de la Escuela Madre.

title: Mr. Softball
description: Susie challenges the campers to a game of softball to get out of doing a chore.

title: Don't Drink the Water
description: In Florida, Ben and Max accidentally come in contact with water from The Fountain of Youth. As a result, Max transforms into a kid and Ben a toddler, with Gwen having to deal with both of them. Our trio then must track down Hex who's found the source of the fountain and prevent him from drinking the water that will make him immortal and unstoppable.

title: The Basketball Liaries
description: With the help from Basketball, Oscar makes an impressive shot that scores him a spot on the Gold League.

title: Momsoon
description: Hedgehog gets a call during her radio show from someone who needs her help.

title: Lellobee Lullaby
description: Come to sing the Lellobee Lullaby! It's nighttime at the farm. Mei and Ella are putting Carlos, Pablo, and Lettie to sleep in the barn. They tuck them in, give them milk and make sure they have their favorite in cuddly toys to snuggle.

title: Food Around the Corner
description: Ben as Gravattack attempts to moderate a fragile peace treaty, but must endure the attacks of tiny alien fleas, which have inhabited his body.

title: Are You My Dad?
description: People are disappearing from Beach City, and Steven tries to solve the mystery.

title: Change Your Mind
description: Steven faces his biggest challenge yet.

title: Sandcastle
description: Blippi and TABBS go to the beach, where they meet Crabby the Crab! A local expert on sandcastles, Crabby teaches them how to build a castle that can't get washed away!

title: Which Watch
description: After a battle with Kevin gets mysteriously cut short, Ben turns his attention to one upping Gwen at Space Camp. But, when his arch-nemesis, Kevin, returns with his sights strangely set on his cousin, our hero must uncover who is really behind it all, Charmcaster!

title: El Hijo de Lilly
description: iLa batalla por el destino de la Montaña Shintaro concluye!

title: Susie Appreciation Day
description: Hedgehog and Oscar find themselves trapped in Susie's cabin and must escape undetected.

title: El Chupacabro
description: El equipo Tennyson descubre que las cabras de una pequeña aldea están siendo aterrorizadas por el legendario Chupacabra. Pero cuando Ben se da cuenta de que en realidad se trata del Dr. Ánimo, nuestro héroe debe frustrar al malvado médico.

title: Juntos Solos
description: Steven organiza una fiesta para reunir a su familia.

title: Popsicle
description: Blippi shrinks down and goes on a sweet and exciting adventure through an ice cream truck with Sherry Pop, a fruit popsicle, finding out that she and all frozen treats need to be in the ice-cold so they won't melt.

title: The Jinxening
description: Craig, Kelsey and JP help a kid who's been jinxed and can't talk, but they soon come to regret it.

title: It's My Party
description: Oscar and Hedgehog plan a surprise birthday party for Susie.

title: Kickflip McPuppycorn
description: Puppycorn wants to impress his skater friends with his sweet skills, except he has none. Hoping to boost his confidence, Unikitty and the gang put on Dr. Fox's invisibility suits to secretly help him pull off impossible moves! But they do their job too well and "pro skater" Puppycorn is invited to showcase his skills in a dangerous stunt competition. How far will the gang go to help the pup live out his rad pipe dreams?

title: Family BBQ
description: Mordecai wants to get a handshake from Margaret's dad.

title: I Am My Mom
description: Steven struggles to fix his mistakes.

title: Helado en 60 segundos
description: Después de que a Owen lo engañan en un camión de helados, los niños se unen para solucionarlo.

title: Apple's Formula
description: Apple needs to find a formula for comedy that will land him a movie role.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Prickly Pair
description: After leaving Little Homeschool, Steven has found a new hobby, plants.

title: A Very Special Episode
description: Rainbow Quartz 2.0 promised to hang out with Onion the same day Sunstone scheduled a home safety Geminar! How can Steven be in two places, and two fusions, at once?

title: Hedgehog Werewolf
description: Hedgehog gets bit by a cute puppy and is starting to act strange.

title: A Tale of Two Ice Bears
description: The Bears accidentally clone Ice Bear and Ice Bear has a hard time adjusting.

title: Ghost the Boy
description: Oscar and Hedgehog befriend a ghost who can't remember who he is.

title: Buggin' the Buggs
description: Team Tennyson travel to the Chrysalen Institute for some hot yoga and good vibes, only to find that the Bugg Brothers are on vacation, too, but are the sneaky insectoids really on holiday, or just cooking up yet another silly, yet high stakes scheme?

title: Sillon
description: Unikitty encuentra una vieja silla reclinable en la acera, pero ve su belleza interior y lo lleva a casa para mostrárselo a la pandilla. En una serie de situaciones absurdas y divertidas, descubrimos cómo una silla sucia e inanimada entra en cada una de sus vidas y las cambia para mejor. Pronto aprendemos que la querida y dulce silla era demasiado buena para este mundo.

title: Sneeze Guard
description: Oscar and Hedgehog must work with the witches to cure Alice's camp-threatening illness.

title: Nuthin' Special/Neighbor Hood
description: Nuthing Special: Frustrated with not knowing what her special power is, Buttercup hunts to discover what makes her special./Neighbor Hood: When everyone on Bubbles' favorite show loses their happy, Bubbles helps bring it back.

title: La Amiga
description: Anaís y Jamie forjan una extraña amistad cuando se las acusa de un crimen que no cometieron.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Radio Silence
description: Oscar must get Hedgehog a special sandwich in order to save their friendship.

title: Sabro Atraco
description: Richard preparó uno de los postres más sabrosos de todos los tiempos, pero lo cerró con llave hasta que los amigos terminen su cena aburrida. Esto no va a seguir así. Para organizar un atraco, Unikitty organiza a sus amigos como un comité de expertos para entrar, salir y comer ese sabroso bocadillo sin que Richard lo sepa. Pero este atraco tiene un traspié. ¿Podrán los amigos llevarse el pastel?

title: Bibi's Do-Over
description: Everyone is ecstatic when Bibi, Batgirl, and Robin capture Toyman and his Do-Over remote - except for Bibi, who failed to stick the landing on a big jump. Unwilling to accept her failure, Bibi uses Toyman's Do-Over remote until she perfects her jump!

title: Meteor Moves
description: Mordecai wants to finally kiss Margaret at a meteor shower.

title: The Great Elf Invention Convention
description: Oscar, Max, and Hedgehog do a favor for Barb the elf in exchange for some chips.

title: Oscar & Hedgehog's Melody
description: Susie holds the annual talent show that has the rest of the campers competing to win.

title: Selfish Shellfish
description: Apple and Onion are faced with a philosophical question: Are they truly doing good deeds for the good of other people or is it all just for them?

title: Divided We Stand
description: While at the beach, Ben discovers a new hero, Ditto, and soon has the ability to create multiple Dittos at once. These multiple Dittos can't agree on anything and drive Gwen crazy. However when the chips are down, these Dittos come together as one fighting force in order to defeat Animo and his army of replicant Stinkflies.

title: The Drama
description: Everyone assumes Darwin and Carrie's relationship is doomed as they're so different. That is, everyone except Darwin and Carrie. When Carrie's cool ghostly ex-boyfriend turns up, Gumball decides to get Darwin to confront what's really going on.

title: The Secret of the Omnitrix Part 2
description: In a battle with Animo, Ben in hero mode, doesn't listen to reason from Max and Gwen, and gets engulfed in a weird energy light. Little does Ben know that the "self destruct" function on the Omnitrix has just been initiated!

title: Shake the Apple Tree
description: It's the end of the summer and the trees are full of delicious apples ready to be picked!

title: Teen Titans Action
description: The Titans learn that toys from comedy shows don't sell, so they become action heroes and are awarded a toy license deal with the Toy Master. But, when they grow tired of the action lifestyle the Titans go on a mission to destroy Toy Master's heavily armed cosmic toy factory to get out of their contract.

title: Ego - Egoista
description: Manzana y Cebolla tienen que demostrar que no son egoístas cuando hacen sus buenas acciones.

title: Country Club
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to rescue the golf cart from a bunch of rich people at a country club.

title: MacGuffin
description: Uncle Grandpa and a kid embark on a dangerous jungle adventure in search of a legendary MacGuffin.

title: The Team Work song
description: Join Ella, Rishi, Heidi, and Bingo in their teamwork making the farm more beautiful and tidy. Working as a team, they do some weeding, they paint the fence and they put some rubbish back into an overturned bin. Soon, the front of the farm is looking neat and they made it work together!

title: Hoyuelitos
description: Raven compite en un certamen de belleza, creyendo que es la forma de reconectarse con su padre.

title: Waffle Cones for Whiffles
description: The Whiffles are too hot and tired to work because their daily treat, colorful ice in Waffles Cones delivered by the whimsical "Icelings," hasn't arrived - the Icelings have mysteriously disappeared. As the Care Bears search for them, Share volunteers to make the treats. It's much more than she can handle but she's determined to go-it-alone and not ask for help. Things get out of hand and Share ends up snared in Bluster's trap with the Icelings, who help her to realize that we get more done when we work together.

title: Daddy's Little Monster
description: Finn and Jake return to the Nightosphere to rescue Marceline and get to the bottom of what's making her act so crazy.

title: Monster Babies
description: Alice lures Oscar and his monster friends for a tea party, but only to turn the monsters into cute babies.

title: Manejo de la ira
description: Para participar de un exitoso programa para niños, Nom Nom debe superar con éxito la prueba de manejo de la ira, con Pardo como compañero.

title: Our Brand is Chaos
description: Bubbles and Buttercup make a deal without realizing the consequences.

title: Tagalong
description: Buttercup is tired of Bubbles following her everywhere.

title: Snow Day
description: Steven and the Crystal Gems get a chance to catch up when they're all snowed in together.

title: Nobody's Perfect
description: When Cheer makes some simple mistakes, she begins to lose confidence in her piloting skills and herself. The self-doubt becomes so severe, she decides to step away from her role as pilot of the Cloudseeker. But the Team needs her, the Whiffles need her, and she must regain her self-confidence so they can stop Bluster's latest nefarious scheme.

title: Ancestor Act
description: When Gumball's sister Anais researches the Watterson family tree, she uncovers a long history of nonsense. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Midnight Quittance
description: Ramona invites Hedgehog and Oscar to participate in a special holiday ritual.

title: The Secret of the Omnitrix Part 3
description: In a battle with Animo, Ben in hero mode, doesn't listen to reason from Max and Gwen, and gets engulfed in a weird energy light. Little does Ben know that the "self destruct" function on the Omnitrix has just been initiated!

title: Spell Crushers
description: Hedgehog tries to get over a crush so she can regain her focus on magic.

title: Jessica La Pasante
description: Fascinada con el Árbol del Trueque y la astucia de Kit para los negocios, Jessica se une a Kit como aprendiz.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol
